---

📋 How to update in the future:

Just change line 4 in sw.js:

```javascript
const APP_VERSION = '2.0.0';  // Change to 2.1.0 or 2.0.1 etc.
```

The footer will automatically show the new version. The service worker cache name will also update automatically.

✅ Verification:

After making these changes:

1. Save all files
2. Clear browser cache (Ctrl+Shift+Delete)
3. Reload the page
4. Check footer shows "Version 2.0.0"
5. Open DevTools → Application → Service Workers → Cache name should show weed-control-v2-0-0

That's it! Only one file to edit (sw.js) for all future updates.
